Reminder App
Requirements : plyer, schedule, and PIL. 
There are two programs inside, "reminder.py" is a simple command line app that runs a predetermined reminder
Program 2 named "reminderAppUi.py" is a program that opens a GUI capable of creating a reminder and having a notification go off at the set interval of time.
The program cannot be closed using the close button if there is an active reminder. it can be minimized through both the top x button or throught he minimize button as well.